# expressions:

`->`, `→`, `>` = to
`*`, `∅` = null
`(...)` = in case of have
`_` = base phoneme of change
`#` = word boundery
`{...}` = set

A > B     / CASE
A B > C D / CASE
{A B} > C / CASE


# sample:
a → e / j_
a → e
w j → gʷ ʒ
{a i u} -> ∅ / _#

j(i) -> i / C_
Ci -> Cʲ / _V
Cu Cw -> Cʷ Cʷ / _V

